#

Chickpea and Quinoa Salad with Avocado Dressing

35 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

MediterraneanAmerican

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing and nutritious salad with protein-packed chickpeas and quinoa, drizzled with a creamy avocado dressing.

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • red onion: 1/4 cup
  • avocado: 1 large
  • lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup
